      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Boom colt HOLLYWOOD STRIP (3) maintained his unbeaten record in proving too speedy for a handy field when resuming in the Simpson Memorial at this circuit and distance. Should be fitter for the outing and he has the gate speed to take advantage of the lower draw so will be very hard to catch. PERFECT STRANGER NZ (2) continued his good form when fourth here last week and came from this barrier to win at this circuit and distance prior. Can make an impact again. ISLA ROCHELLE (8) kept her manners in check last week and did a much better job for second. Draws wider but should be close to her peak third-up off a let-up. TUKAHA (7) only missed narrowly in a higher-graded race at Wagga last start and scored at this circuit and distance prior. Draws wider but deserves respect.",
